body:
Boyfriend!Jin

I may or may not have forgotten that I even did these but here’s Jin for you :)

Boyfriend!Jin

  • What a man!
  • On your phone he’d be like “Handsome❣️” and trust me he put that in himself
  • On his phone you’re “Y/N💕”
  • He’s really nice he’s like a caring bf
  • + a lot of jokes skdkskdks
  • If he sees a chance he’ll whip out a joke or and start doing that squeaky laugh
  • You find it real funny tho
  • I mean who wouldn’t- it’s Jin
  • “Jin, sTOp you’re too funny!”
  • He really appreciates it tho
  • He loves making you smile
  • He’d DEF take you out on food dates
  • FooOoooOoooOoOooD
  • He’d be up for taking you to all sorts of restaurants and cafes
  • Like any and EVERY cuisine
  • Chinese, Japanese, Caribbean, Cuban
  • Go for it
  • He’d also love to film you guys eat
  • A lil EatJin&Y/N video yk yk
  • Delicious food, a handsome man and amazing Y/N
  • Best food duo amirite
  • And he’d def spoil you
  • Food or anything else
  • Spoil spoil spoilt lil s.o
  • At home he’s eager to try and cook new things
  • He’d ask you to help him
  • Unless you’re Namjoon level at cooking, then he’d ask you stay out of the kitchen skdksk
  • Or sometimes he wants to surprise with like hybrid foods idk
  • If you’re cooking
  • He likes to backhug you while you cook
  • Whatever it is, it’s usually good
  • Protective?
  • He’s not really that protective
  • He’s really free
  • Jealous?
  • Nah
  • Spooning?
  • I don’t see him as much of a spooner
  • But I see him liking some contact while you nap/sleep
  • He always makes you feel really comfortable
  • His amazing self confidence rubs off on you a while into the relationship
  • And you love yourself too which is wonderful <3
  • So that’s TWO LOVELY PEOPLE IN A HOUSEHOLD YAAAAY
  • When he introduces you to BTS
  • He’d crack a joke or pun and introduce you
  • Or just say smth really funny like the idiot he is
  • “I’ve got a beautiful/good looking face to match my amazing handsome one, meet Y/N!”
  • Skdkks sTOP JiN
  • Anyway
  • Bangtan will love you
  • And most importantly
  • Wonder how you cope with his dad jokes and puns
  • And weirdness
  • But someone has to
  • They secretly love their hyung tho and you know that
  • He’d def great you right
  • He’s really a gentleman
  • You’ll always feel loved with Mr Kim Seokjin

summary: (Random declaration of love for JJK incoming) Aah I love this boy so damn much~! I pray that he finds happiness in life and that...
body:
(Random declaration of love for JJK incoming)

Aah I love this boy so damn much~!

I pray that he finds happiness in life and that he will never have to let go of his passions. I pray that his talents will never go un-appreciated, that he will receive ten times the amount of love and support he gives to others. I pray that should his pretty doe eyes ever tear up, they do so out of happiness and love, and not out of sorrow and despair, that he would never go a day without experiencing the warmth of being loved by others. I hope he will never be tainted by this cruel world, that he be accepted for who he is by the people that matter to him, that he loves himself wholly and learns to accept and learn from his mistakes rather than drown in them. Life is unfair and he is still so young yet he’s had to go through so much to get to where he is now, and I pray that he only grows stronger from now on, mentally and emotionally. 

I hope he learns to accept himself first and foremost.

In some alternate reality, I’ve adopted him as my little brother and we share banana milk and cookies every night while talking about BTS, his videos and how cute Jimin-ssi’s butt is (don’t judge us)

The boy reminds me of myself when I was his age and that seriously scares me sometimes, how close he could get to becoming a mess like me…

I pray he becomes stronger and never succumbs to his inner fears. I pray he swims and never sinks.

I wish people would see and accept his soft, delicate side. He tries so hard to be what others ask of him but he’s nervous and scared that he’ll mess up and disappoint. He has so much love for his hyungs and his family and his fans, but he gets judged harshly sometimes, be it when he expresses too little or too much. People say he’s the undefeated golden boy with an infinite skillset, but in reality he’s just dedicated and passionate and works very hard at what he does. He’s relentless in his quest to perfect his creations and that’s what makes him shine the most. Talent will never prosper without hard work and dedication to back it up, and Jeon Jungkook succeeds because he does just that.

I pray that the special someone in his life will never fail to tell him how amazing he is and how much he is loved and cherished. I pray that the people he trusts and reaches out to will never leave him waiting for their hand, will never leave him to brave the storm alone. Be it his family, his hyungs, his company, his fans his loved ones. Be it he himself. 

I pray that he grows to love all of himself, both good and bad. I pray that he survives, that he lives.

Goddanggit I love this precious kid to bits…TT
